🚀 Getting Started

Visit the Platform: Navigate to 12th Board Hub
Select Your Stream: Choose between Arts, Commerce, or Science
Download Notes: Get handwritten notes for your subjects
Start Learning: Begin with important concepts and practice questions
Track Progress: Use PYQs to assess your preparation

📱 How to Use

Login (if required) to access personalized learning
Browse the subject-wise notes by stream
Download high-quality handwritten notes
Practice with important questions and PYQs
Watch reference videos for better understanding

